					</ab>
					<ab xml:lang="pli-Latn">
						<lb n="1"/>namo dhaṁmmo svakhyāto bhagavata dham<supplied reason="lost">mo</supplied> <space type="horizontal" quantity="1" unit="character"/> sanditthiko Akaliko Ehipassiko paccataṁ viñuhi ti
