						<lb n="1"/>Indriyaparopariyatte ñāṇaṁ ◊ buddhañānaṁ satta Anusaññāyanaṁ buddhañānaṁ U<supplied reason="lost">ju</supplied>patipanno bhagavato
					</ab>
